{"tid":1477132,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[手繪短片] 幫朋友出Post，整咗段片支持前線","createTime":"2019-08-16T04:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T08:50:06.000Z","uid":52804,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa6b35fe26d9976f7ad6e656bc2350d0d6f6696","tid":1477132,"uid":52804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"代友出post<br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\n幾乎每次遊行我都有去，但我身形大份，行動力好差，所以唔敢上前線，怕會拖累大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一次幫手傳物資同開遮時，見到前線勇武、FA、甚至記者，我都好想同你哋講多謝，所以整咗一段片，希望大家總有一日可以喺煲底高呼自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107472760596530/videos/300440620787032/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107472760596530%2Fvideos%2F300440620787032%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=5f6f1c92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107472760596530/videos/300440620787032/</a><br />\n<br />\n揀咗首歌叫「心照一生」，我覺得好適合前線，香港人，加油！818維園見！"},{"pid":"b06b6e455524d03feb6cf68f08498563b7fc35af","tid":1477132,"uid":52804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5035a558e5e8ffd4b92495136d31e9bf269fae","tid":1477132,"uid":52804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6009817643991ac0c06132630278133d01256685","tid":1477132,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"以任何形式為香港付出既人都值得支持"},{"pid":"19305693fdf2971c563592a3d5579b924ed4ebf0","tid":1477132,"uid":52804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5653e29d63c04489835e97